data.description: 5BR/3BA/3Car Garage, Perfect home for creating great family memories and/or entertaining. Kitchen has 2 pantries, double oven, large island, fridge stays. 3 fireplaces (living room, master suite & back patio). Master BR is unbelievable w/ a sitting area+office. Unique Upgrades..electrical outlets in the eaves of the home, a separate breaker for the hot tub, another breaker in the garage for an xtra freezer/fridge, water filtration system, 2 pergolas, gazebo, lights, 10x12 shed on slab, Xtra stamped concrete, fire pit, outside shower, TV w/ cover & firestick stay, outside wifi extender (for those that want to relax while working from home), Xtra PVC conduit pipe buried under patio for adding electricity to shed if want. Washer/Dryer stay. USDA
